/zhuangbei/1273644924970.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />圣殿指环|105|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273742490796.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />魔瓶|11|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273544321268.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />魔杖|110|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273742813195.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />回城卷轴|','64|<img src=\"http://i2.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/52735b1641663584.jpg\" />胖子|57|<img src=\"http://i1.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/52735a86ed95649779.jpg\" />混沌骑士|48|<img src=\"http://i3.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/52735987618d473495.jpg\" />熊战士|','小精灵的缺点就是脆，相当脆，而且自身能力较弱，需要有队友陪同才能发挥作用。','36|<img src=\"http://i1.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/5273584c9650391537.jpg\" />秀逗魔导士|85|<img src=\"http://i3.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/52735d341bb5883103.jpg\" />巫妖|35|<img src=\"http://i1.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/527357fe0462875317.jpg\" />沉默术士|','83|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273740853846.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />铁树枝干|83|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273740853846.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />铁树枝干|104|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273742427429.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />艾西菲的|103|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273742335363.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />瓶装蓝色|83|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273740853846.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />铁树枝干|80|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273740712719.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />食人魔力|','<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299037200122.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299037157337.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299037254333.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299037200122.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attac