的情况下推荐裸圣殿+大罐子，主烈火精灵回复很足','出门装：凤凰的技能耗蓝不高，但是由于凤凰自身是力量英雄，所以小净化还是要带一带。现在的几个技能都会消耗凤凰自身的血量，所以回血道具一定要多带。中期装：由于凤凰改版后单杀能力丧失殆尽，只能充当一个团战辅助，他尤其是由于一技能，出肉装减伤在所难免。但是先锋盾由于远程效果不好，所以不推荐大家出。可以先买一个1100的球撑血，靠静谧鞋或者挑战回血，后期用球转龙心。另外，骨灰盒对于丧失自身恢复能力的凤凰而言，值得考虑。鞋类选择：静谧鞋60% 假腿40% ，不太推荐新版凤凰使用秘法鞋。用静谧鞋取代先锋盾的回血效果是是首选。假腿显得就过于中庸。神装：凤凰后期以肉盾吸收伤害，团战扔光技能后放大爬起来再来第二套技能为主。所以主要走肉装，除了以上装备，天堂之戟也是适合凤凰特点的装备。'),(18,'海民的定位是控制，游走，gank，海民打dps有点虚，他没有站着原地跟别人A的资本，所以说还是配合队友去gank抓人吧，海民的机动性比较强，配合队友抓人效果非常明显，不过有时候略显坑爹。','16|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273545411155.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />远行鞋|67|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273739657610.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />洛萨之锋|27|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273649866185.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />Guinsoo的邪|35|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273652047170.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />强袭装甲|57|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273738303263.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />圣剑|37|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273652501957.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />黑皇杖|','8|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273543684164.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />假腿|42|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273653447823.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />先锋盾|105|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273742490796.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />魔瓶|67|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273739657610.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />洛萨之锋|11|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273544321268.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />魔杖|110|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273742813195.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />回城卷轴|','11|<img src=\"http://i2.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/527355603e6ae18870.jpg\" />山岭巨人|6|<img src=\"http://i3.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/527354ac4f2aa18769.jpg\" />半人马酋长|93|<img src=\"http://i3.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/52735cb77cecb80537.jpg\" />半人猛犸|66|<img src=\"http://i2.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/52735b43438ca12808.jpg\" />鱼人守卫|56|<img src=\"http://i3.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/52735a787fb7e92776.jpg\" />斧王|','海民的缺点就是后期乏力，用不好就是团灭的机器，改版后雪球的滚动速度变慢有点鸡肋了，而且很怕敌人开BKB，比较蛋疼的就是带着队友滚到坑里。','74|<img src=\"http://i3.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/52735bfb12e7f7873.jpg\" />影魔|58|<img src=\"http://i1.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/52735a95dabdb49637.jpg\" />末日使者|35|<img src=\"http://i1.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/527357fe0462875317.jpg\" />沉默术士|','83|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273740853846.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />铁树枝干|83|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273740853846.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />铁树枝干|83|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273740853846.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />铁树枝干|104|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273742427429.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />艾西菲的|103|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273742335363.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />瓶装蓝色|73|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273740167832.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />圆盾|','<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299044951316.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299044903877.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299044903877.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299044951316.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299044903877.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299045045890.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299044903877.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299044951316.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299044951316.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://imag