当肉基本上没有可能了，因为现在的DOTA战斗节奏十分快，还没有等你肉起来你的老家都没有了，所以说更多的gank和杀人才是正道。','16|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273545411155.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />远行鞋|36|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273652242948.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />魔龙之心|24|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273648739199.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />卡嘉之洞|39|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273652751557.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />希瓦的守|27|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273649866185.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />Guinsoo的邪|33|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273651222720.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />Aghanim的神|','14|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273545099828.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />相位靴|105|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273742490796.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />魔瓶|24|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273648739199.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />卡嘉之洞|11|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273544321268.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />魔杖|110|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273742813195.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />回城卷轴|','49|<img src=\"http://i1.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/527359a9c65de98731.jpg\" />复仇之魂|28|<img src=\"http://i2.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/527357108efd186664.jpg\" />水晶室女|10|<img src=\"http://i3.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/5273554ed2a9568811.jpg\" />流浪剑客|','屠夫是一个单杀高手，如果等级上面领先了很多杀人可以说都是一套秒你。所以说多插眼做好视野是十分重要的，兽王、发条地精、chen、炸弹人这些英雄也能很好的预防屠夫的gank，因为它们的技能都有开视野的作用，当然了如果你有逃脱技能也可以，只要对方的屠夫有一点点失误你就可以逃跑了。','5|<img src=\"http://i2.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/527354935582f29789.jpg\" />兽王|52|<img src=\"http://i2.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/52735a060410471849.jpg\" />地精工程师|58|<img src=\"http://i1.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/52735a95dabdb49637.jpg\" />末日使者|','80|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db