a/skill/1299050597483.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299050700104.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299050597483.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299050667784.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299050667784.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299050667784.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299050700104.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299050637246.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299050637246.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299050637246.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299050637246.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299050700104.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1302161569867.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1302161569867.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1302161569867.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1302161569867.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1302161569867.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1302161569867.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1302161569867.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1302161569867.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1302161569867.jpg\" />','这是一个比较稳妥的加点，能在线上混，还能用1技能给对方造成伤害去配合队友击杀对方。同时有着吸血能保证一个线上回复能力和推线能力。当然还有一种加点方式是1技能和黄点对加，这样的加点在线上就是很抗打，团战的时候还能当个T冲上去，只要有重生就可以。','出门装：补刀斧或者双拳套配合一点恢复装备很不错的，混到6级你就是再生侠了。中期装：散华和碎骨锤都是一个效果留人，雷锤和狂战就是为了混线收钱用的。中期的骷髅王其实已经有一定的战斗实力了，因为自带暴击和吸血效果所以还是很IMBA的。鞋类选择：踏实的出假腿吧，攻速攻击都有还能撑血对骷髅王来说是最好的选择了。神装：这套装备的SNK输