/1299051060470.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299051007154.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299050959184.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299050959184.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299050959184.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299051060470.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299050909688.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299050909688.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299050909688.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1302161569867.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299051060470.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1302161569867.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1302161569867.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1302161569867.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1302161569867.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1302161569867.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1302161569867.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1302161569867.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1302161569867.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1302161569867.jpg\" />','尸王的噬魂非常强大，但是前期由于没有过多的单位，高级别的噬魂毫无意义。所以最多点到两级足够。我们只学一级D来满足偷力量的效果，然后迅速满墓碑参与团推，低级别的墓碑无论是持续时间还是耐打程度都完全不够。这种加点方法适合于大招流团队推进。','出门装：虽然写了很多装备，主要他出装可以双拳套转骨灰盒。或者上来就是圆盾肉起，带恢复出门。当然圣殿也是很好的，推线当肉就是你的目标。中期装：这里列出了7件装备，除了祭品是带线用的，剩下都是给尸王自己加属性或者撑肉的。因为尸王蓝比较少，所以推荐出秘法鞋。鞋类选择：相位鞋是必须的，更快的移动速度能让你多打对方几下，初始攻击不算差，力量成长也很高。还有就是你的火必须配合上高移动速度才有意义。神装：什么叫肉死你不偿命，这就是！你看到这样的尸王你还想干它么？蓝杖尸王相当于给队友每个人出了一个大件，如此的BUG存在，神也撼动不了它的身躯。'),(72,'潮汐猎人的定位就是一个半肉半gank的英雄，蹲人并不太可取。线上发育，只要有机会就扔1技能配合队友击杀对面英雄。','16|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273545411155.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />远行鞋|95|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273741647647.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />科勒的匕|36|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273652242948.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />魔龙之心|63|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273739278422.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />狂战斧|35|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273652047170.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />强袭装甲|59|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273738599120.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />辉耀|','8|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273543684164.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />假腿|95|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273741647647.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />科勒的匕|11|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273544321268.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />魔杖|110|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273742813195.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />回城卷轴|45|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273653894140.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />挑战头巾|','10|<img src=\"http://i3.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/5273554ed2a9568811.jpg\" />流浪剑客|49|<img src=\"http://i1.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/527359a9c65de98731.jpg\" />复仇之魂|28|<img src=\"http://i2.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/527357108efd186664.jpg\" />水晶室女|','其实潮汐真的不用克制，你不可能永远不让潮汐到6对么，它就算打酱油，只要到了6级一样可以团战。而且如果刻意去遏制潮汐的发育，那他们的后期不管了么？所以潮汐不需要克制，只要躲好它的大就可以了。如果说真要克制的话就只有一个末日使者了。','58|<img src=\"http://i1.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/52735a95dabdb49637.jpg\" />末日使者|35|<img src=\"http://i1.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/527357fe0462875317.jpg\" />沉默术士|','83|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273740853846.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />铁树枝干|83|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachmen