有追杀有逃命，在没有跳刀之前放大的必备先手，7级必满（注意走位尽量双插甚至三插四插）；前期最好加一点沙尘暴用于保命（躲指向性技能，隐身），由于需要持续施法且单位伤害不高，之后三级可以最后再加；沙王前期缺魔，所以最好加一两点黄点撑属性；腐蚀毒是带线神技，中期加满；大是高伤害AOE技能，有大加大。','出门装：回复为主,如果出了两个拳套就是后面合成骨灰盒子用的。中期装：这套装备让你有足够的回蓝了，并且有了跳刀团战也够了。瓶子看队友吧，中SOLO的队友一般都会有瓶子的，别去抢了，有个骨灰就很不错了。鞋类选择：秘法鞋很适合沙王，第一沙王用穿刺加尸毒清兵很快，其次还有就是沙王辅助很好用，秘法鞋能帮队友回蓝很不错。神装：可能看着这套装备很脆，但是能出来就已经很不错了，你是个辅助。这套对你来说神的不能再神了。只要队友给点力，不会到你出着身就结束了。'),(76,'血魔是一个纯gank型选手，一个推推棒一个刃甲，当然如果你富裕再来一个红杖保证你是单杀王。多配合队友杀人很容易，还有1技能的禁魔也要给好。','16|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273545411155.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />远行鞋|59|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273738599120.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />辉耀|36|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273652242948.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />魔龙之心|58|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273738470993.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />金箍棒|64|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273739366488.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />幻影斧|60|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273738861759.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />蝴蝶|','14|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273545099828.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />相位靴|42|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273653447823.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />先锋盾|43|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273653594194.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />刃甲|11|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273544321268.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />魔杖|110|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273742813195.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />回城卷轴|','83|<img src=\"http://i2.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/52735d405ba0526717.jpg\" />恶魔巫师|10|<img src=\"http://i3.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/5273554ed2a9568811.jpg\" />流浪剑客|49|<img src=\"http://i1.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/527359a9c65de98731.jpg\" />复仇之魂|','血魔的每次gank大的效果都很明显，如果想克制血魔，从一开始对中就要压制暗影萨满、恶魔巫师、风暴之灵、蝙蝠骑士这种单中的英雄压制能力都比较强，而且速瓶子后能够相当凶狠的消耗血魔的血量，因为血魔一般不会带很多恢复的。还有就是血魔跟夜魔很像，毕竟都是魔字辈儿的。如果两三次gank都没有成功，那血魔就差不多前期小费掉了。','58|<img src=\"http://i1.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/52735a95dabdb49637.jpg\" />末日使者|35|<img src=\"http://i1.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/527357fe0462875317.jpg\" />沉默术士|','79|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273740581754.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />压制之刃|104|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273742427429.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />艾西菲的|83|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273740853846.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />铁树枝干|83|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273740853846.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />铁树枝干|83|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273740853846.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />铁树枝干|103|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273742335363.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />瓶装蓝色|','<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299066705858.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299066814721.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299066914484.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299066914484.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299066914484.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299067009806.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299066914484.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299066814721.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299066814721.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299066814721.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299067009806.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299066705858.jpg\" /> \n<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/skill/1299066705858.jpg\"