45411155.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />远行鞋|27|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273649866185.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />Guinsoo的邪|36|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273652242948.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />魔龙之心|35|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273652047170.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />强袭装甲|24|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273648739199.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />卡嘉之洞|','8|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273543684164.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />假腿|25|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273649109222.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />影之灵龛|42|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273653447823.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />先锋盾|11|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273544321268.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />魔杖|110|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273742813195.jpg\" class=\"ico2\" />回城卷轴|','10|<img src=\"http://i3.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/5273554ed2a9568811.jpg\" />流浪剑客|91|<img src=\"http://i2.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/52735d90c25f079748.jpg\" />暗影恶魔|80|<img src=\"http://i3.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/52735cf09fea154211.jpg\" />祸乱之源|','死灵龙的低级别C蓝耗是硬伤。另外过分需要操作，导致控制能力不稳定是该英雄门槛过高缺乏人气的原因。小龙在后期容易被人点掉也会导致他的威力大打折扣。死灵飞龙的优势在于守墓人斗篷的额外魔抗和护甲，所以打死灵龙千万不要用高伤害爆发技能直接招呼。尽量先用持续伤害（毒类）或者普攻打掉他的四层防御再爆发。所以剧毒术士、VIP等英雄对于去除死灵龙防御层非常有帮助。团战中一定要优先拔掉死灵龙，方法是AOE技能和普攻打掉死灵龙防御层之后爆发秒杀。所以高物理输出，尤其是减甲技能非常重要。比如小黑、德鲁伊、狼人等英雄在团战中击杀死灵龙比较容易。但是就限制死灵龙而言，神圣伤害技能直接打死小龙是完美的方法。比如修补匠的激光，痛苦之源的B等等。','58|<img src=\"http://i1.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/52735a95dabdb49637.jpg\" />末日使者|35|<img src=\"http://i1.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/527357fe0462875317.jpg\" />沉默术士|80|<img src=\"http://i3.static.olcdn.com/dota/db/2013/11/01/52735cf09fea154211.jpg\" />祸乱之源|','80|<img src=\"http://image6.766.com/db/attachments/dota/zhuangbei/1273740712719.gif\" class=\"ico2\" />食人魔力|80|<im